          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0348P0_20000412_WH_52'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-keith-hill' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0348P0_20000412_WH_52' title='Link to this speech by Mr Keith Hill' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-keith-hill" title="Mr Keith Hill">Mr. Hill</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I am afraid that I do not have time to give way.</p><p>
            Without those partnerships, we shall find it much more difficult to achieve the vision that I have outlined for our waste strategy.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
